import React, { Component } from "react";
import Slider from "react-slick";
import "slick-carousel/slick/slick.css";
import "slick-carousel/slick/slick-theme.css";

export default class SimpleSlider extends Component {
    render() {
        const settings = {
            dots: true,
            infinite: true,
            speed: 500,
            slidesToShow: 1,
            slidesToScroll: 1
        };
        return ( <
            div >
            <
            h2 > Single Item < /h2> <
            Slider {...settings } >
            <
            div >
            <
            h3 > 1 < /h3> <
            /div> <
            div >
            <
            h3 > 2 < /h3> <
            /div> <
            div >
            <
            h3 > 3 < /h3> <
            /div> <
            div >
            <
            h3 > 4 < /h3> <
            /div> <
            div >
            <
            h3 > 5 < /h3> <
            /div> <
            div >
            <
            h3 > 6 < /h3> <
            /div> <
            /Slider> <
            /div>
        );
    }
}
